window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Including brand new material, this is the complete collection of Rebus short stories from the <i>Sunday Times</i> Number one best seller. </b></p> <p>Over the years, Ian Rankin has amassed an incredible portfolio of short stories. Published in crime magazines, composed for events, broadcast on radio, they all share the best qualities of his phenomenally popular Rebus novels. </p> <p>Brought together for the first time, and including brand-new material, this is the ultimate Rebus short-story collection and a must-have book for crime lovers and for Ian's millions of fans alike. No Rankin aficionado can go without it.</p>"; 
